Parkway Drive - Ire (2015)

Ire is the upcoming fifth studio album by Australian metalcore band Parkway Drive. The album is expected to be released on 25 September 2015, through Resist Records and Epitaph Records.

Promotion and release

Ire was announced on 8 June 2015, along with the release of the first song from the album, "Vice Grip", and its music video. On August 24, the band released a second song, "Crushed", also accompanied by a video. On September 14, the band released a third song, "The Sound of Violence".
Touring

Parkway Drive have announced they will be touring through Australia, New Zealand, North America and Europe in support of Ire.
